name: Мега-Болл
text: Look at the top 7 cards of your deck. You may reveal a Pokémon you find there and put it into your hand. Shuffle the other cards back into your deck.

name: Hop
text: Draw 3 cards.

name: Hyper Potion
text: Heal 120 damage from 1 of your Pokémon that has at least 2 Energy attached. If you healed any damage in this way, discard 2 Energy from it.

name: Kabu
text: Shuffle your hand into your deck. Then, draw 4 cards. If your Active Pokémon is your only Pokémon in play, draw 8 cards instead.

name: Marnie
text: Each player shuffles their hand and puts it on the bottom of their deck. If either player put any cards on the bottom of their deck in this way, you draw 5 cards, and your opponent draws 4 cards.

name: Milo
text: Discard up to 2 cards from your hand, and draw 2 cards for each card you discarded in this way.

name: Piers
text: Search your deck for an Energy card and a Darkness Pokémon, reveal them, and put them into your hand. Then, shuffle your deck.

name: Покешар

name: Эликсир

name: Professor's Research

name: Rotom Bike

name: Rotom Phone
text: Look at the top 5 cards of your deck, choose 1 of them, and shuffle the other cards back into your deck. Then, put the card you chose on top of your deck.

name: Sonia

name: Suspicious Food Tin

name: Team Yell Grunt
